              def prepare_document_photo(document, is_local, is_thumbnail=true)
        
      349. 
      
        
    349. 
          
          
                  document.image_name = ''
        
      350. 
      
        
    350. 
          
          
                  document.is_draft = is_local
        
      351. 
      
        
    351. 
          
          
                    unless document.attached_photo_ids.nil? || document.attached_photo_ids.empty?
        
      352. 
      
        
    352. 
          
          
                        if document.attached_photo_ids.start_with?('S') || is_local == false
        
      353. 
      
        
    353. 
          
          
                            #what is going on here?
        
      354. 
      
        
    354. 
          
          
                            document_photo = Photo.where(temp_id: document.attached_photo_ids.sub(/[S]/, ' ').to_i).first
        
      355.

      356. 
      
        
    356. 
          
          
                                if is_thumbnail
        
      357. 
      
        
    357. 
          
          
                                    document.image_name = 'http://pantone201.ca/webskins/olp/photos/thumbnails/' + document_photo.id.to_s + "_" + document_photo.riding_id.to_s + document_photo.filename + '_Thumbnail.jpg'
        
      358. 
      
        
    358. 
          
          
                                else
        
      359. 
      
        
    359. 
          
          
                                    document.image_name = 'http://pantone201.ca/webskins/olp/photos/' + document_photo.id.to_s + "_" + document_photo.riding_id.to_s + document_photo.filename + '_PhotoUp.jpg'
        
      360. 
      
        
    360. 
          
          
                                end
        
      361. 
      
        
    361. 
          
          
                            end
        
      362. 
      
        
    362.

              def prepare_document_author(document, thumbnail=true)
        
      388. 
      
        
    388. 
          
          
                  if !document.author.nil? && document.author.start_with?("@c#", "@m#", "@p#", "@v#")
        
      389. 
      
        
    389. 
          
          
                      author = nil
        
      390. 
      
        
    390. 
          
          
                      author_photo_dir = nil
        
      391. 
      
        
    391. 
          
          
                      if document.author.start_with?("@c#")
        
      392. 
      
        
    392. 
          
          
                          document.author["@c#"] = " "
        
      393. 
      
        
    393. 
          
          
                          author = Author.find_by_id(document.author.to_i)
        
      394. 
      
        
    394. 
          
          
                          author_photo_dir = 'olp'
        
      395. 
      
        
    395. 
          
          
                      elsif document.author.start_with?("@m#")
        
      396. 
      
        
    396. 
          
          
                          # not used now
        
      397. 
      
        
    397. 
          
          
                          document.author = ''
        
      398. 
      
        
    398. 
          
          
                      elsif document.author.start_with?("@p#")
        
      399. 
      
        
    399. 
          
          
                          # not used now
        
      400. 
      
        
    400. 
          
          
                          document.author = ''
        
      401. 
      
        
    401. 
          
          
                      elsif document.author.start_with?("@v#")
        
      402. 
      
        
    402. 
          
          
                          document.author["@v#"] = " "
        
      403. 
      
        
    403. 
          
          
                          author = CandidateAuthor.find_by_id(document.author.to_i)
        
      404. 
      
        
    404. 
          
          
                          author_photo_dir = 'vote'
        
      405. 
      
        
    405. 
          
          
                      end
        
      406. 
      
        
    406. 
          
          
                      if author != nil
        
      407. 
      
        
    407. 
          
          
                          if @language == 'FR'
        
      408. 
      
        
    408. 
          
          
                              document.author = author.name_fr + ", " + author.role_fr
        
      409. 
      
        
    409. 
          
          
                          else
        
      410. 
      
        
    410. 
          
          
                              document.author = author.name_en + ", " + author.role_en
        
      411. 
      
        
    411. 
          
          
                          end
        
      412. 
      
        
    412. 
          
          
                          if thumbnail
        
      413. 
      
        
    413. 
          
          
                              document.author_photo = 'http://pantone201.ca/webskins/' + author_photo_dir + '/photos/author/thumbnails/' + author.id.to_s + "_" + author.riding_id.to_s + author.filename + '_Thumbnail.jpg'
        
      414. 
      
        
    414. 
          
          
                          else

              def random_key_string(length=16)
        
      518. 
      
        
    518. 
          
          
                  chars = 'abcdefghjkmnpqrstuvwxyz'
        
      519. 
      
        
    519.

                  key

              def full_name_to_short(full_name='')
        
      525. 
      
        
    525. 
          
          
                  short_name = 'default'
        
      526. 
      
        
    526. 
          
          
                  if full_name.strip != ''
        
      527. 
      
        
    527. 
          
          
                      start_index = 0
        
      528. 
      
        
    528. 
          
          
                      index = full_name.index(' ', start_index)
        
      529. 
      
        
    529. 
          
          
                      while index != nil && index > 0
        
      530. 
      
        
    530. 
          
          
                          start_index = index + 1
        
      531. 
      
        
    531. 
          
          
                          index = full_name.index(' ', start_index)
        
      532. 
      
        
    532. 
          
          
                      end
        
      533. 
      
        
    533. 
          
          
                      if start_index > 0
        
      534. 
      
        
    534. 
          
          
                          short_name = full_name[0].downcase + full_name[start_index..(full_name.length-1)].downcase
        
      535. 
      
        
    535. 
          
          
                      end
        
      536. 
      
        
    536. 
          
          
                      short_names = short_name.split('\'')
        
      537. 
      
        
    537. 
          
          
                      if short_names.length > 1 then short_name = short_names[0] + short_names[1] else short_name = short_names[0] end
        
      538. 
      
        
    538. 
          
          
                  end
        
      539. 
      
        
    539. 
          
          
                  short_name
        
      540. 
      
        
    540. 
          
          
              end

              def datetime2string(dt=DateTime.now)
        
      617. 
      
        
    617. 
          
          
                  year_str = dt.year.to_s
        
      618. 
      
        
    618. 
          
          
                  month_str = dt.month.to_s
        
      619. 
      
        
    619. 
          
          
                  if dt.month < 10 then month_str = '0' + month_str end
        
      620. 
      
        
    620. 
          
          
                  day_str = dt.day.to_s
        
      621. 
      
        
    621. 
          
          
                  if dt.day < 10 then day_str = '0' + day_str end
        
      622. 
      
        
    622. 
          
          
                  hour_str = dt.hour.to_s
        
      623. 
      
        
    623. 
          
          
                  if dt.hour < 10 then hour_str = '0' + hour_str end
        
      624. 
      
        
    624. 
          
          
                  minute_str = dt.min.to_s
        
      625. 
      
        
    625. 
          
          
                  if dt.min < 10 then minute_str = '0' + minute_str end
        
      626. 
      
        
    626. 
          
          
                  second_str = dt.sec.to_s
        
      627. 
      
        
    627. 
          
          
                  if dt.sec < 10 then second_str = '0' + second_str end
        
      628. 
      
        
    628. 
          
          
                  dt_str = year_str + "-" + month_str + "-" + day_str + " " + hour_str + ":" + minute_str + ":" + second_str
        
      629. 
      
        
    629. 
          
          
                  dt_str
        
      630. 
      
        
    630. 
          
          
              end

    292. 
          
          
                      riding_news_documents = PlaDocument.find(:all, :order => "document_date DESC", :conditions => {:riding_id => riding_id, :doctype => (0..1), :published => true, :language => language, :expiry_date => DateTime.now..(DateTime.now+3650)})
        
      293. 
      
        
    293. 
          
          
                      central_news_documents = Document.find(:all, :order => "document_date DESC", :conditions => {:riding_id => 0, :doctype => (0..1), :published => true, :publish_on_pla => true, :language => language, :expiry_date => DateTime.now..(DateTime.now+3650)})
        
      294. 
      
        
    294. 
          
          
                      customized_managements = PlaCustomizedManagement.find(:all, :order => "id", :conditions => {:riding_id => riding_id, :central_table => "documents"})
        
      295. 
      
        
    295. 
          
          
                      if customized_managements != nil && customized_managements.length > 0 && central_news_documents != nil && central_news_documents.length > 0
        
      296. 
      
        
    296. 
          
          
                          customized_managements.each do |customized_management|
        
      297. 
      
        
    297. 
          
          
                              central_news_documents.each do |news_document|
        
      298. 
      
        
    298. 
          
          
                                  if news_document.id == customized_management.central_record_id
        
      299. 
      
        
    299. 
          
          
                                      news_document.headline = customized_management.local_headline_en
        
      300. 
      
        
    300. 
          
          
                                      news_document.published = customized_management.is_local_published
        
      301. 
      
        
    301. 
          
          
                                      if news_document.published == false
        
      302. 
      
        
    302. 
          
          
                                          central_news_documents.delete(news_document)
        
      303. 
      
        
    303. 
          
          
                                      end
        
      304. 
      
        
    304. 
          
          
                                  end
        
      305. 
      
        
    305. 
          
          
                              end
        
      306. 
      
        
    306. 
          
          
                          end
        
      307. 
      
        
    307. 
          
          
                      end
        
      308. 
      
        
    308. 
          
          
                      top_news_documents = Array.new
        
      309. 
      
        
    309. 
          
          
                      while (riding_news_documents != nil && riding_news_documents.length > 0) || (central_news_documents != nil && central_news_documents.length > 0)
        
      310. 
      
        
    310. 
          
          
                          if riding_news_documents == nil || riding_news_documents.length <= 0
        
      311. 
      
        
    311. 
          
          
                              central_news_documents[0].is_draft = false
        
      312. 
      
        
    312. 
          
          
                              top_news_documents << central_news_documents[0]
        
      313. 
      
        
    313. 
          
          
                              central_news_documents.delete_at(0)
        
      314. 
      
        
    314. 
          
          
                          elsif central_news_documents == nil || central_news_documents.length <= 0
        
      315. 
      
        
    315. 
          
          
                              riding_news_documents[0].is_draft = true
        
      316. 
      
        
    316. 
          
          
                              top_news_documents << riding_news_documents[0]
        
      317. 
      
        
    317. 
          
          
                              riding_news_documents.delete_at(0)

              def normalize_text_url_break_tag(str_txt)
        
      671. 
      
        
    671. 
          
          
                  if str_txt == nil then str_txt = '' end
        
      672. 
      
        
    672. 
          
          
                  str_lst = (((str_txt.gsub("\r\n", "\n")).gsub("\n", " <br /> ")).gsub("\r", " <br /> ")).split(' ')
        
      673. 
      
        
    673. 
          
          
                  str_txt = ''
        
      674. 
      
        
    674. 
          
          
                  str_lst.each do |str|
        
      675. 
      
        
    675. 
          
          
                      if str.start_with?("http://", "https://")
        
      676. 
      
        
    676. 
          
          
                          str_txt += '<a href="' + str + '" target="_blank">' + str + '</a> '
        
      677. 
      
        
    677. 
          
          
                      elsif str.start_with?("www.")
        
      678. 
      
        
    678. 
          
          
                          str_txt += '<a href="http://' + str + '" target="_blank">' + str + '</a> '
        
      679. 
      
        
    679. 
          
          
                      else
        
      680. 
      
        
    680. 
          
          
                          str_txt += str + ' '
        
      681. 
      
        
    681. 
          
          
                      end
        
      682. 
      
        
    682. 
          
          
                  end
        
      683. 
      
        
    683. 
          
          
                  str_txt
        
      684. 
      
        
    684. 
          
          
              end
        
      685. 
      
        
    685. 
          
          
          
        
      686. 
      
        
    686. 
          1
          
              def localized_date_str(dt, lan, include_weekday=false)
        
      687. 
      
        
    687. 
          
          
                  dt_str = dt.strftime('%B %d, %Y')
        
      688. 
      
        
    688. 
          
          
                  if include_weekday then dt_str = dt.strftime('%A, %B %d %Y') end
        
      689. 
      
        
    689. 
          
          
                  if lan == 'FR'
        
      690. 
      
        
    690. 
          
          
                      if dt.mon == 1
        
      691. 
      
        
    691. 
          
          
                          dt_str = "le " + dt.day.to_s + " janvier " + dt.year.to_s
        
      692. 
      
        
    692. 
          
          
                      elsif dt.mon == 2
        
      693. 
      
        
    693. 
          
          
                          dt_str = "le " + dt.day.to_s + " f&eacute;vrier " + dt.year.to_s
        
      694. 
      
        
    694. 
          
          
                      elsif dt.mon == 3
        
      695. 
      
        
    695. 
          
          
                          dt_str = "le " + dt.day.to_s + " mars " + dt.year.to_s
        
      696. 
      
        
    696. 
          
          
                      elsif dt.mon == 4
        
      697. 
      
        
    697. 
          
          
                          dt_str = "le " + dt.day.to_s + " avril " + dt.year.to_s
        
      698. 
      
        
    698. 
          
          
                      elsif dt.mon == 5
        
      699. 
      
        
    699. 
          
          
                          dt_str = "le " + dt.day.to_s + " mai " + dt.year.to_s
        
      700. 
      
        
    700. 
          
          
                      elsif dt.mon == 6

              def unicode_to_utf8(unicode_string)
        
      793. 
      
        
    793. 
          
          
                  unicode_string.gsub(/\\u\w{4}/) do |s|
        
      794. 
      
        
    794. 
          
          
                      str = s.sub(/\\u/, "").hex.to_s(2)
        
      795. 
      
        
    795. 
          
          
                      if str.length < 8
        
      796. 
      
        
    796. 
          
          
                          CGI.unescape(str.to_i(2).to_s(16).insert(0, "%"))
        
      797. 
      
        
    797. 
          
          
                      else
        
      798. 
      
        
    798. 
          
          
                          arr = str.reverse.scan(/\w{0,6}/).reverse.select{|a| a != ""}.map{|b| b.reverse}
        
      799. 
      
        
    799. 
          
          
                          hex = lambda do |s|
        
      800. 
      
        
    800. 
          
          
                              (arr.first == s ? "1" * arr.length + "0" * (8 - arr.length - s.length) + s : "10" + s).to_i(2).to_s(16).insert(0, "%")
        
      801. 
      
        
    801. 
          
          
                          end
        
      802. 
      
        
    802. 
          
          
                          CGI.unescape(arr.map(&hex).join)
        
      803. 
      
        
    803. 
          
          
                      end
        
      804. 
      
        
    804. 
          
          
                  end
        
      805. 
      
        
    805. 
          
          
              end
        
      806. 
      
        
    806. 
          
          
           
        
      807.

              def utf8_to_unicode(string) # :nodoc:

                  '\\u'+string.unpack("U*").map{|c|"%04x" %c}.join('\\u')
        
      813.

              def format_twitter_content(twitter_content)

            def find_or_create_user(current_user)
        
      45. 
      
        
    45. 
          
          
              if current_user && self.user == current_user
        
      46. 
      
        
    46. 
          
          
                # User logged in and the identity is associated with the current user
        
      47. 
      
        
    47.

      48. 
      
        
    48. 
          
          
              elsif current_user && self.user != current_user
        
      49. 
      
        
    49.

      50. 
      
        
    50. 
          
          
                # so lets associate the identity and update missing info
        
      51.
